OL,6,FTwo men charged with arson after an
OL,7,Fattack at a mosque in East Sussex
OL,8,Fearlier this month have appeared in
OL,9,Fcourt.
OL,11,FTwo people were inside the mosque in
OL,12,FPeacehaven when the incident occurred
OL,13,Fon October 4.
OL,15,FThe front entrance of the mosque and
OL,16,Ftwo cars were damaged.
