OL,4,Con mosque remanded in custody
OL,6,FRicky Ryder, 38, of Richington Way in
OL,7,FSeaford, and Jack Slowey, 34, of
OL,8,FMayfield Avenue in Peacehaven, have
OL,9,Fboth been charged with arson with
OL,10,Fintent to endanger life.
OL,12,FBoth men appeared at Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Friday and spoke
OL,14,Fto confirm their names, addresses and
OL,15,Fdates of birth.
OL,17,FDavid Burns, prosecuting, said: "Both
OL,18,Fof the gentlemen who were inside the
OL,19,Fmosque were able to smell smoke and
OL,20,Fget out in time."
