OL,6,FRyder and Slowey were remanded in
OL,7,Fcustody ahead of their next hearing at
OL,8,Fthe Old Bailey on November 14.
OL,10,FSussex Police said a 42-year-old man
OL,11,Ffrom Peacehaven, who was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of arson with intent to
OL,13,Fendanger life, has been released on
OL,14,Fconditional bail.
OL,16,FAlmost #50,000 has been raised on
OL,17,FGoFundMe from the community for the
OL,18,Fmosque to help rebuild and repair the
OL,19,Fdamage.
