OL,6,FOn Thursday, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer announced an additional #10
OL,8,Fmillion in security funding to protect
OL,9,FMuslim communities from hate crimes
OL,10,Fand attacks following a visit with
OL,11,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood to the
OL,12,FPeacehaven Mosque.
OL,14,FThe investment for mosques and Muslim
OL,15,Ffaith centres will provide security
OL,16,Fmeasures including CCTV, alarm
OL,17,Fsystems, secure fencing and security
OL,18,Fstaff, the Government said.
OL,20,FSir Keir said: "Britain is a proud and
OL,21,Ftolerant country.
