OL,6,F"Attacks on any community are attacks
OL,7,Fon our entire nation and our values.
OL,9,F"This funding will provide Muslim
OL,10,Fcommunities with the protection they
OL,11,Fneed and deserve, allowing them to
OL,12,Flive in peace and safety.
OL,14,F"I want a Britain built for all and my
OL,15,FGovernment is committed to delivering
OL,16,Fsafer streets for everyone ` and that
OL,17,Fmeans protecting places of worship
OL,18,Ffrom those who seek to divide us
OL,19,Fthrough hate and violence."
